<span>What can I bring with me to the festival?</span>
<div class="m-questions__answer-btn">A</div>
<div class="hidden m-questions__answer-text" data-answer-number="12">
The following items will be prohibited from entering the venue. Prohibited items are as follows:
<li>NO Weapons of any kind including poles and sticks</li>
<li>NO Fireworks or explosives</li>
<li>NO Illegal substances of any kind</li>
<li>NO Outside food or drink. 1 Factory sealed water bottle up to 1 Liter is allowed</li>
<li>NO Pets (Except Service Animals per ADA guidelines)</li>
<li>NO Flyers, Posters, Handbills, Stickers (No Solicitation)</li>
<li>NO Chairs</li>
<li>NO Glass of any kind</li>
<li>NO Skateboards, Scooters, Bicycles or Motorized vehicles</li>
<li>NO Coolers (hard or soft unless for medical reasons)</li>
<li>NO Professional recording devices including Cameras with detachable lenses, video or audio</li>
<li>NO Glowsticks</li>
<li>NO Laser Pointers</li>
<li>NO Large signs, kites, Stuffed animals (including backpacks), Totems.</li>
<li>NO Any item that can obstruct viewing.</li>
<li>NO Masks of any kind that obstruct or partially obstruct the face. (Religious headwear O.K.)</li>
<li>NO Any item deemed by security as a risk to public safety</li>
<li>NO Framed backpacks</li>
<li>NO Drugs</li>
<li>NO Alcohol</li>
<li>NO unauthorized Vending of Products</li>
<li>NO Instruments</li>
<li>NO Spray Paint</li>
<li>NO Balls, Balloons, Frisbees</li>
<li>NO Bottles or Cans (except 1 Factory sealed water bottle up to 1 Liter is allowed)</li>
<li>NO Sealed Packages</li>
<li>NO Ladders, stepstools or Bota Bags</li>
<li>NO Flags, Signs or Banners regardless of size</li>
<li>Allowed items as follows:</li>
<li>YES (1) Factory sealed water bottle up to 1 liter</li>
<li>YES Sunscreen</li>
<li>YES Empty water containers for refill inside including camelbacks</li>
<li>YES Bags non-framed (all bags will be tagged)</li>
<li>YES Selfie Stick</li>
</div>
</a>
